0(Amendment)%20Bill%20and%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reorganisation%20(Amendment)%20Bill.%20He%20countered%20Trinamool%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20(TMC)%20Saugata%20Roy%20who%20had%20said%20%E2%80%9Cone%20flag%2C%20one%20prime%20minister%2C%20one%20constitution%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20political%20slogan%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Shah%20wondered%20how%20a%20country%20could%20have%20two%20prime%20ministers%2C%20two%20constitutions%2C%20and%20two%20flags.%20He%20added%20that%20it%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20political%20slogan%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20his%20party%20firmly%20believes%20in%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhosoever%20did%20it%20was%20wrong.%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20corrected%20it.%20Your%20approval%20or%20disagreement%20does%20not%20matter.%20The%20entire%20country%20wanted%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20countered%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20questioned%20the%20government%20over%20introducing%20amendments%20to%20the%20Bill%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20yet%20to%20deliver%20its%20verdict%20on%20the%20Article%20370%20case.%20The%20apex%20court%20concluded%2016%20days%20of%20hearings%20in%20the%20case%20in%20September.%20The%20court%20is%20expected%20to%20pronounce%20its%20verdict%20sometime%20this%20month.%20Article%20370%20gave%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20the%20power%20to%20have%20a%20separate%20constitution%2C%20a%20state%20flag%2C%20and%20autonomy%20of%20internal%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20National%20Conference%20MP%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%20sought%20to%20know%20from%20the%20government%20why%20did%20it%20not%20conduct%20elections%20if%20felt%20the%20situation%20was%20peaceful%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20He%20alleged%20that%20no%20attempt%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20restore%20statehood%20as%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20legislature%20in%202018%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20been%20under%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%2C%20prompting%20local%20political%20parties%20to%20demand%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20resume%20electoral%20activities%20in%20the%20Union%20territory.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20official%20statements%2C%20the%20delay%20is%20due%20to%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20local%20unit%20wanting%20to%20defer%20the%20exercise%20at%20least%20till%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20polls%2C%20as%20it%20is%20not%20yet%20ready%20to%20face%20any%20polls%20even%20local%20body%20polls%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20previous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flet-alone-assembly-polls-even-local-body-elections-unlikely-in-jk-before-2024%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2014%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20lieutenant%20governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20had%20said%20that%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-local-body-polls-wont-be-held-anytime-soon-lg-makes-it-official%5C%22%3Eelections%20to%20the%20urban%20local%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20be%20delayed%20considerably.%20The%20tenure%20of%C2%A0Srinagar%20Municipal%20Corporation%20ended%20on%20November%205%20while%20the%20Jammu%20civic%20body%20completed%20its%20five-year%20tenure%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%2014.%20Other%20municipal%20bodies%20across%20the%20Union%20territory%20will%20finish%20their%20tenure%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month.%C2%A0The%20last%20ULB%20and%20panchayat%20elections%20in%20the%20UT%20were%20held%20between%20October%20and%20December%202018%20%E2%80%93%20which%20too%20were%20after%20a%20long%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701841126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F13152628%2F3475958106_0cdd457c3a_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fready-for-jk-elections-onus-on-election-commission-to-announce-schedule-centre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20legislature%20in%202018%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20been%20under%20the%20President's%20Rule.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20official%20statements%2C%20there%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Union%20territory%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20face%20polls%20anytime%20soon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fready-for-jk-elections-onus-on-election-commission-to-announce-schedule-centre%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%3A%20Hotels%20prepare%20for%20tourism%20surge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701841038000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105773203%2Cimgsize-57382.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fram-mandir-inauguration-major-hotel-chains-gear-up-to-benefit-from-expected-tourism-boom%2Farticleshow%2F105772474.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20approaches%2C%20hotel%20chains%20and%20investors%20are%20eyeing%20the%20city%20for%20potential%20growth.%20The%20development%20of%20infrastructure%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20expected%20to%20benefit%20the%20hospitality%20and%20travel%20services%20sector.%20Several%20hotel%20chains%2C%20including%20IHCL%2C%20Marriott%2C%20Sarovar%20Hotels%20%26amp%3B%20Resorts%2C%20and%20Wyndham%20Hotels%20%26amp%3B%20Resorts%2C%20have%20already%20signed%20deals%20for%20hotels%20in%20Ayodhya.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Sparks%20Are%20Few%20And%20Far%20Between%20In%20Musical%20Thriller%20Chamak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20gap%20that%20separates%20ostensible%20intent%20from%20actual%20content%20isn't%20exactly%20yawning%20in%20%3Ci%3EChamak%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20a%20SonyLIV%20series%20created%2C%20co-written%20and%20directed%20by%20Rohit%20Jugraj%20but%20the%20little%20that%20does%20exist%20takes%20some%20of%20the%20sheen%20off%20the%20musical%20thriller.%20Its%20sparks%20are%20not%20only%20few%20and%20far%20between%2C%20they%20aren't%20bright%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudded%20with%20a%20complement%20of%20songs%20that%20range%20from%20the%20peppy%20to%20the%20soulful%2C%20from%20the%20romantic%20to%20the%20radical%2C%20the%20six-episode%20series%20often%20gropes%20for%20the%20right%20rhythm.%20It%20attempts%20a%20deep%20dive%20into%20the%20Punjabi%20popular%20music%20scene%20and%20its%20social%20context%20but%20fails%20to%20break%20free%20from%20generic%20revenge%20saga%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EChamak%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20a%20concoction%20of%20love%2C%20crime%2C%20vengeance%2C%20social%20fissures%20and%20music%20that%20wades%20through%20superfluities.%20Some%20of%20its%20key%20plot%20points%20are%20gratuitously%20stretched%2C%20while%20other%20equally%20crucial%20strands%20of%20the%20storyline%20are%20glossed%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20is%20embellished%20with%20pop%20and%20hip-hop%20numbers%20composed%2Fsung%20by%20a%20galaxy%20of%20Punjabi%20stars%20and%20curated%20and%20produced%20by%20the%20showrunner%20himself.%20Sadly%2C%20the%20narrative%20does%20not%20quite%20match%20the%20highs%20that%20the%20music%20achieves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aspiring%20singer%20flees%20Vancouver%20after%20an%20act%20of%20violence%20-%20an%20impetuous%20response%20to%20heartbreak%20-%20lands%20him%20in%20trouble%20with%20the%20law%20in%20Canada.%20He%20reaches%20Chandigarh%20and%20stumbles%20upon%20a%20secret%20that%20sends%20his%20life%20into%20another%20tailspin%20that%20constitutes%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EChamak%3C%2Fi%3E%20approximates%20the%20meandering%20course%20and%20wayward%20nature%20of%20the%20protagonist's%20struggles.%20The%20narrative%20ricochets%20between%20the%20extremes%20of%20the%20realities%20of%20the%20industry%20and%20the%20tumult%20in%20the%20beleaguered%20young%20man's%20heart%20as%20he%20battles%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20his%20tragic%20family%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaala%20(Paramvir%20Singh%20Cheema)%20grapples%20with%20the%20rough%20and%20tumble%20of%20the%20music%20industry%20even%20as%20he%20seeks%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20truth%20behind%20the%20assassination%20of%20popular%20pop%20singer%20Tara%20Singh%20(Gippy%20Grewal%20in%20a%20special%20appearance)%20nearly%20twenty-five%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20water%20has%20flown%20down%20the%20Beas%20since%20the%20violent%20incident%2C%20but%20Kaala%2C%20with%20some%20help%20from%20drummer%20and%20wannabe%20singer%20Jasmine%20%26quot%3BJazz%26quot%3B%20Narula%20(Isha%20Talwar)%2C%20an%20independent%20woman%20he%20meets%20by%20chance%20and%20develops%20a%20romantic%20relationship%20with%2C%20is%20determined%20to%20find%20the%20killers%20of%20Tara%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20conveniently%20swept%20the%20case%20under%20the%20carpet%20for%20good%20but%20a%20doughty%20old%20journalist%20Gurpal%20Singh%20(Kuljeet%20Singh)%20hasn't%20given%20up%20hope%20of%20figuring%20out%20what%20led%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Tara%20Singh.%20Kaala%20makes%20common%20cause%20with%20the%20latter%2C%20who%20has%20heaps%20of%20newspaper%20clippings%2C%20recordings%20and%20concert%20posters%20related%20to%20the%20life%20and%20times%20of%20the%20slain%20singer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journo's%20reportage%20suggests%20three%20likely%20scenarios%20-%20a%20terrorist%20strike%2C%20an%20honour%20killing%20or%20a%20betrayal%20by%20associates.%20Armed%20with%20the%20scribe's%20fount%20of%20information%2C%20Kaala%20begins%20to%20ferret%20around%20for%20further%20clues.%20Predictably%2C%20powerful%20people%20do%20not%20want%20the%20truth%20to%20come%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaala%20is%20a%20singer%2C%20not%20a%20crime%20investigator.%20The%20role%20is%20forced%20upon%20him%20by%20circumstances.%20It%20assumes%20increasing%20importance%20as%20he%20descends%20into%20a%20quagmire%20of%20intrigue%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20which%20is%20a%20thriving%20music%20label%20Teeja%20Sur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-g-GckbcJJA%3Fsi%3DFZxuw-ndwfV39vTL%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20run%20by%20the%20temperamental%20Pratap%20Deol%20(Manoj%20Pahwa)%20with%20the%20aid%20of%20three%20children%20who%20he%20does%20not%20quite%20trust%20-%20Jai%20(Dhanveer%20Singh)%2C%20Guru%20(Mohit%20Malik)%20and%20Naaz%20(Ankita%20Goraya).%20The%20old%20man's%20disdain%20is%20directed%20particularly%20at%20Guru%20because%20the%20latter%20isn't%20the%20kind%20of%20son%20that%20he%20expects%20the%20boy%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaala's%20sights%20are%20set%20on%20a%20career%20in%20music%20but%20his%20investigation%20is%20repeatedly%20deflected%20from%20his%20calling.%20Somebody%20tells%20him%20that%20he%20must%20achieve%20success%20as%20a%20singer%20if%20he%20wishes%20to%20find%20what%20he%20is%20looking%20for%20-%20the%20men%20responsible%20for%20the%20elimination%20of%20Tara%20Singh%20a%20quarter%20century%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinger%20Mika%20Singh%2C%20playing%20himself%2C%20reminds%20Kaala%20that%20though%20he%20has%20a%20powerful%20voice%20it%20is%20only%20when%20he%20becomes%20a%20powerful%20man%20will%20he%20be%20able%20to%20ensure%20that%20he%20gets%20way.%20Music%20takes%20the%20form%20of%20a%20tool%20of%20vendetta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20show%2C%20Kaala%20squares%20off%20against%20MC%20Square%20in%20an%20impromptu%20rap%20contest%20outside%20a%20bar%20where%20he%20is%20employed%20as%20a%20valet.%20The%20video%20goes%20viral%20and%20helps%20him%20grab%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20industry.%20But%20his%20big%20break%20is%20still%20some%20distance%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJealousy%20and%20self-interest%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20when%20Kaala%20teams%20up%20with%20Lata%20Brar%20(Akasa%20Singh)%2C%20only%20daughter%20of%20a%20reclusive%20music%20guru%2C%20Jugal%20Brar%20(Suvinder%20Vicky)%2C%20to%20deliver%20his%20first%20hit.%20The%20struggling%20Jazz%20does%20not%20take%20kindly%20to%20being%20left%20out%20in%20the%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EChamak%3C%2Fi%3E%20explores%20in%20a%20frustratingly%20mechanical%20manner%20the%20quest%20for%20stardom%20in%20a%20demanding%20industry%20and%20the%20dynamics%20of%20power%20in%20the%20business%20of%20talent%20spotting%20and%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaala%20is%20stranded%20in%20two%20separate%20terrains.%20One%20is%20represented%20by%20the%20repercussions%20of%20the%20assassination%2C%20the%20other%20by%20the%20obstacles%20he%20faces%20on%20the%20career%20front%20where%20vested%20interests%20can%20make%20or%20break%20fortunes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EChamak%3C%2Fi%3E%20refers%20tangentially%20to%20Tara%20Singh%20being%20a%20revolutionary%20singer%20who%20took%20on%20the%20establishment.%20The%20journalist%20who%20tracked%20his%20career%20points%20out%20to%20Kaala%20that%20there%20is%20no%20diversity%20or%20equality%20in%20the%20media%20business.%20Only%20dominant%20segments%20of%20the%20society%20get%20to%20tell%20their%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20of%20the%20two%20angles%20-%20an%20artiste's%20non-conformism%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20representation%20in%20journalism%20-%20is%20explored%20beyond%20a%20point.%20That%20leaves%20many%20potentially%20significant%20themes%20untapped%20in%20a%20show%20that%20could%20definitely%20have%20done%20with%20greater%20depth%20and%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParamvir%20Singh%20Cheema%2C%20last%20seen%20in%20a%20supporting%20role%20in%20Tabbar%20(also%20on%20SonyLIV)%2C%20fits%20the%20ro