20Most%20Powerful%20Women%20List.%20She%20Ranks...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20has%20ranked%2032nd%20in%20the%20Forbes'%20list%20of%20world's%20most%20powerful%20women%20that%20also%20featured%20US%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20musician%20Taylor%20Swift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20other%20Indian%20women%20named%20in%20the%20list%20are%20HCL%20Corporation%20CEO%20Roshni%20Nadar%20Malhotra%20(rank%2060)%2C%20Steel%20Authority%20of%20India%20chairperson%20Soma%20Mondal%20(rank%2070)%2C%20and%20Biocon%20founder%20Kiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20(rank%2076).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEuropean%20Commission%20chief%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20topped%20the%20list%2C%20followed%20by%20European%20Central%20Bank%20boss%20Christine%20Lagarde%20at%20the%20second%20position%20and%20US%20Vice%20President%20Kamal%20Harris%20at%20number%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20became%20India's%20first%20full-time%20Finance%20Minister%20in%20May%202019%20and%20also%20heads%20the%20Corporate%20Affairs%20ministry.%20She%20held%20roles%20at%20UK's%20Agricultural%20Engineers%20Association%20and%20BBC%20World%20Service%20before%20joining%20politics%2C%20Forbes%20said.%20She%20has%20also%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Malhotra%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20HCL%20founder%20and%20industrialist%20Shiv%20Nadar.%20As%20the%20chairperson%20of%20HCL%20Technologies%2C%20she's%20responsible%20for%20all%20strategic%20decisions%20for%20the%20company%2C%20Forbes%20said.%20She%20took%20over%20the%20role%20from%20her%20father%20in%20July%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mondal%20is%20the%20first%20woman%20chairperson%20of%20the%20state-run%20Steel%20Authority%20of%20India%20(SAIL)%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%20Having%20assumed%20the%20role%20in%202021%2C%20she%20has%20led%20the%20steelmaker%20to%20record%20financial%20growth%2C%20her%20profile%20read%2C%20as%20the%20firm's%20p