se%20who%20abstain%20from%20this%20have%20a%20problem.%20I%20only%20requested%20%5Bthe%20officials%5D.%20They%20say%20I%20spoke%20loudly.%20I%20have%20a%20sore%20throat%E2%80%A6%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20spoke%20that%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20Acharya%20clarified%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20only%20requested%20the%20officials%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20food%20was%20covered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20anyone%20felt%20bad%2C%20I%20apologise.%20This%20was%20not%20for%20any%20particular%20category%20%5Bof%20people%5D%E2%80%A6.%20I%20am%20working%20according%20to%20respected%20PM%20Modiji%E2%80%99s%20vision.%20We%20want%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20trust%20and%20collective%20development%20of%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BJP%20MLA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fworking-according-to-pm-modijis-vision-rajasthan-bjp-mla-backs-off-meat-closure%2Fcid%2F1984843%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20poultry%20sellers%20were%20seen%20shutting%20their%20shops%20on%20Monday%20after%20Acharya%20and%20his%20supporters%20asked%20the%20police%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20shops%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20up%20an%20unidentified%20official%20in%20front%20of%20TV%20cameras%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fworking-according-to-pm-modijis-vision-rajasthan-bjp-mla-backs-off-meat-closure%2Fcid%2F1984843%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CCan%20non-veg%20be%20sold%20openly%20on%20the%20road%3F%20Answer%20yes%20or%20no.%20So%2C%20you%20support%20this.%20All%20roadside%20non-veg%20stalls%20should%20be%20shut%20down%20immediately.%20I%20will%20take%20the%20report%20from%20you%20in%20the%20evening.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20care%20who%20the%20officer%20is.%E2%80%9D%20The%20conversation%20ended%20with%20his%20supporters%20chanting%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Jai%20Shree%20Ram%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20popular%20Hindutva%20slogan%20often%20used%20for%20establishing%20religious%20superiority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20of%20Civil%20Liberties%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20veg%20and%20non-veg%20in%20the%20Street%20Vendors%20Act.%20There%20is%20a%20rule%20to%20create%20vending%20zones%20and%20provide%20security%20to%20street%20vendors%20by%20constituting%20a%20town%20vending%20committee.%20Till%20now%2C%20the%20town%20vending%20committee%20has%20not%20provided%20protection%20to%20the%20vendors.%20Licences%20have%20not%20been%20given%20to%20vendors%20and%20vending%20zones%20have%20also%20not%20been%20identified.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20a%20newly%20elected%20MLA%20taking%20the%20law%20into%20his%20hands%20and%20threatening%20meat%20shops%20and%20non-veg%20street%20vendors%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20great%20concern.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20unheard%20of%20in%20Rajasthan.%20It%20seems%20like%20the%20MLA%E2%80%99s%20individual%20bravado%20rather%20than%20a%20planned%20action.%20My%20sense%20is%20that%20he%20was%20pulled%20up%20by%20senior%20leaders%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaipur-based%20political%20analyst%20Sunny%20Sebastian%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701839509000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06103243%2FScreenshot-2023-12-06-at-10.30.47-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frajasthan-bjp-mla-who-shut-down-meat-shops-a-day-after-election-win-apologises%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Videos%20of%20the%20MLA's%20heated%20exchange%20with%20municipal%20officials%20and%20police%20went%20viral.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frajasthan-bjp-mla-who-shut-down-meat-shops-a-day-after-election-win-apologises%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bus%20plunges%20into%20a%20ravine%20killing%2016%20i