risk%20from%20tipping%20points%20that%20could%20unleash%20a%20domino%20effect%20of%20irreversible%20catastrophes%20across%20the%20planet%2C%20researchers%20warned%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20comprehensive%20assessment%20ever%20conducted%20of%20Earth's%20invisible%20tripwires%20was%20released%20as%20leaders%20meet%20for%20UN%20climate%20talks%20in%20Dubai%20with%202023%20set%20to%20smash%20all%20heat%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20of%20the%2026%20tipping%20points%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20report%20--%20such%20as%20melting%20ice%20sheets%20--%20are%20linked%20to%20global%20warming%2C%20other%20human%20activities%20like%20razing%20swathes%20of%20the%20Amazon%20rainforest%20could%20also%20push%20Earth's%20ecosystems%20to%20the%20brink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20of%20these%20are%20showing%20signs%20of%20tipping%20--%20from%20melting%20ice%20sheets%20threatening%20catastrophic%20sea%20level%20rise%2C%20to%20mass%20die-off%20of%20tropical%20coral%20reefs%20--%20the%20report%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20may%20have%20already%20begun%20to%20irrecoverably%20transform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20world%20crosses%20the%20threshold%20for%20just%20one%20tipping%20point%2C%20dealing%20with%20the%20immediate%20humanitarian%20disaster%20could%20distract%20attention%20away%20from%20stopping%20the%20others%2C%20creating%20a%20%26quot%3Bvicious%20cycle%26quot%3B%20of%20mass%20hunger%2C%20displacement%20and%20conflict%2C%20the%20report%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETim%20Lenton%2C%20an%20Earth%20system%20scientist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Exeter%20and%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20report%2C%20told%20AFP%20that%20these%20tipping%20points%20pose%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20of%20a%20magnitude%20that%20is%20unprecedented%20for%20humanity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20not%20all%20bad%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20highlighted%20a%20range%20of%20positive%20tipping%20points%20--%20such%20as%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20renewable%20energy%20and%20changing%20to%20plant-based%20diets%20--%20that%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20swiftly%20build%20momentum%20and%20tip%20things%20back%20the%20other%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20leaning%20back%20on%20a%20chair%20to%20that%20balance%20point%20where%20a%20small%20nudge%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20Lenton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20end%20up%20sprawled%20on%20your%20back%20on%20the%20floor%20--%20or%20if%20you're%20lucky%2C%20back%20upright.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20brink%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20concern%20is%20if%20the%20melting%20West%20Antarctic%20and%20Greenland%20ice%20sheets%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20raise%20sea%20levels%20two%20metres%20by%202100%2C%20exposing%20nearly%20half%20a%20billion%20people%20to%20frequent%20coastal%20flooding%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Greenland%20ice%20sheet%20has%20been%20shrinking%20at%20such%20a%20rate%20that%20it%20might%20already%20be%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20it%20past%20the%20tipping%20point%20or%20could%20it%20stop%20shrinking%3F%20No%20one's%20quite%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20Lenton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20three%20tipping%20points%20most%20at%20risk%20are%20dying%20tropical%20coral%20reefs%2C%20melting%20permafrost%20and%20an%20ocean%20current%20called%20the%20North%20Atlantic%20subpolar%20gyre%20circulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20ocean%20tipping%20point%20is%20the%20Atlantic%20Meridional%20Overturning%20Circulation%20(AMOC)%2C%20a%20vast%20system%20that%20regulates%20the%20global%20transfer%20of%20heat%20from%20the%20tropics%20into%20the%20northern%20hemisphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20report%20said%20it%20was%20plausible%20--%20though%20unlikely%20--%20that%20the%20AMOC%20would%20collapse%20this%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20destabilising%20change%20could%20lead%20to%20vast%20regions%20getting%20far%20less%20rain%2C%20potentially%20halving%20the%20area%20worldwide%20where%20wheat%20and%20corn%20can%20be%20grown%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20that%20goes%2C%20suddenly%20there%20will%20be%20a%20global%20food%20security%20crisis%20and%20comparable%20water%20crisis%20as%20major%20monsoon%20systems%20in%20the%20tropics%20basically%20fail%20in%20India%20and%20West%20Africa.%20That%20will%20be%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%2C%26quot%3B%20Lenton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Dire'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20massive%20fires%20in%20the%20Amazon%20rainforest%20and%20Canada's%20boreal%20forests%20suggest%20they%20are%20also%20more%20immediately%20at%20risk%20of%20tipping%20than%20previously%20thought%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenton%20compared%20the%20job%20of%20the%20more%20than%20200%20researchers%20who%20created%20the%20over-400%20page%20Global%20Tipping%20Points%20Report%20to%20risk%20assessors%20analysing%20a%20new%20aeroplane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAMOC%20collapsing%20was%20like%20spotting%20something%20that%20could%20cause%20that%20plane%20to%20%26quot%3Bfall%20out%20of%20the%20sky%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20redesign%20the%20Earth%20to%20make%20it%20safer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECo-author%20Manjana%20Milkoreit%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Oslo%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bour%20global%20governance%20system%20is%20inadequate%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20coming%20threats%20and%20implement%20the%20solutions%20urgently%20required.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20called%20for%20tipping%20points%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20global%20stocktake%20being%20debated%20at%20the%20COP28%20talks%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20national%20targets%20to%20combat%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20urged%20more%20effort%20to%20push%20tipping%20points%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%20such%20as%20changing%20policies%20o