C%20the%20events%20surrounding%20Lennon's%20shooting%20by%20obsessed%20fan%20Mark%20David%20Chapman%20on%20December%208%2C%201980%2C%20and%20its%20aftermath%20are%20thoroughly%20examined.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20delves%20into%20various%20conspiracy%20theories%20that%20emerged%20after%20Lennon's%20death%20and%20includes%20audio%20recordings%20of%20Chapman%20discussing%20his%20case%20with%20his%20lawyers%20during%20parole%20applications.%20The%20title%20highlights%20the%20fact%20that%20Chapman%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20second-degree%20murder%20just%20before%20his%20trial%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%2020-year%20prison%20sentence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Farts-entertainment%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjohn-lennon-last-words-mark-david-chapman-b2458561.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJay%20Hastings%20who%20worked%20at%20the%20front%20desk%20of%20the%20Dakota%20building%20in%20New%20York%2C%20where%20the%20musician%20lived%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Yoko%20Ona%20and%20their%20song%20Sean%20Ono%20Lennon%20recalled%20the%20fateful%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20runs%20past%20me.%20He%20goes%2C%20'I'm%20shot%2C'%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hastings%20recalls%20in%20the%20documentary.%20%26quot%3BHe%20had%20blood%20coming%20out%20of%20his%20mouth.%20He%20just%20collapsed%20on%20the%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20half%20rolled%20him%20to%20his%20back%20and%20took%20his%20glasses%20off%2C%20put%20them%20on%20the%20desk.%20And%20Yoko%20was%20screaming%2C%20'Get%20an%20ambulance%2C%20get%20an%20ambulance%2C%20get%20an%20ambulance.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Taxi%20driver%20named%20Richard%20Peterson%20also%20witnessed%20the%20shooting%20while%20sitting%20in%20his%20parked%20car%20outside%20the%20building.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLennon%20was%20walking%20in%20and%20this%20kid%20says%2C%20'John%20Lennon%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20chunky%20guy.%20I'm%20looking%20at%20him%20through%20the%20front%20window%20of%20my%20cab.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20looking%20at%20him%20shoot%20him.%20This%20guy%20just%20shot%20John%20Lennon.%20I%20thought%20they%20were%20making%20a%20movie%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20see%20no%20lights%20or%20cameras%20or%20anything%20so%20I%20realised%2C%20'Hey%2C%20this%20ain't%20no%20movie.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-part%20documentary%20will%20reveal%20shocking%20details%20of%20Lennon's%20tragic%20murder%2C%20The%20Independent%20reported.%20It%20will%20interviews%20with%20some%20of%20his%20closest%20friends%2C%20along%20with%20Chapman's%20defence%20lawyers%2C%20psychiatrists%2C%20detectives%20and%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chapman%20was%20asked%20why%20he%20shot%20Lennon%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B'All%20You%20Need%20Is%20Love'%2C%20have%20you%20ever%20heard%20that%3F%20Well%2C%20this%20is%20what%20I%20say%20to%20that%3A%20all%20you%20need%20is%20love%20and%20250%20million%20dollars.%20He%20was%20the%20biggest%2C%20phoniest%20bastard%20that%20ever%20lived.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChapman%2C%2068%2C%20is%20currently%20being%20held%20at%20Green%20Haven%20Correctional%20Facility%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20his%202020%20hearing%2C%20he%20apologised%20to%20Lennon's%20widow%2C%20Ono%2C%20and%20called%20the%20shooting%20a%20%26quot%3Bdespicable%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20selfish%26quot%3B%20act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20sorry%20for%20the%20pain%20that%20I%20caused%20to%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20about%20it%20all%20of%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20new%20Beatles%20song%20produced%20with%20a%20little%20help%20from%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20including%20the%20vocals%20of%20John%20Lennon%20was%20recently%20released.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20helped%20isolate%20late%20member%20