n%20Indian%20history%20for%20one%20more%20reason.%20It%20was%20on%20another%20December%206%20%E2%80%93%20in%201992%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished.%20Former%20president%20and%20the%20then-vice%20president%20Dr%20K.R.%20Narayanan%20has%20described%20this%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20greatest%20tragedy%20India%20faced%20after%20the%20assassination%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Ftheprint-profile%2Fkr-narayanan-the-president-who-didnt-hesitate-to-call-a-spade-a-spade%2F317705%2F%5C%22%3EMahatma%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Ftheprint-profile%2Fkr-narayanan-the-president-who-didnt-hesitate-to-call-a-spade-a-spade%2F317705%2F%5C%22%3EG%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Ftheprint-profile%2Fkr-narayanan-the-president-who-didnt-hesitate-to-call-a-spade-a-spade%2F317705%2F%5C%22%3Eandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20event%20has%20inflicted%20deep%20wounds%20on%20the%20psyche%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%2C%20who%20had%20reposed%20their%20faith%20in%20constitutional%20values%20and%20institutions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20suggested%20by%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20in%20his%20speech%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20on%20November%2025%2C%201949%2C%20equality%2C%20liberty%20and%20fraternity%20cannot%20be%20divorced%20from%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWithout%20equality%2C%20liberty%20would%20produce%20the%20supremacy%20of%20the%20few%20over%20the%20many.%20Equality%20without%20liberty%20would%20kill%20individual%20initiative.%20Without%20fraternity%2C%20liberty%20and%20equality%20could%20not%20become%20a%20natural%20course%20of%20things.%20It%20would%20require%20a%20constable%20to%20enforce%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feparlib.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F763285%2F1%2Fcad_25-11-1949.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDr%20Ambedkar%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Babri%20demolition%20is%20a%20crime%2C%20but%20not%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20could%20be%20punished%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20after%20a%20prolonged%20trial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20title%20case%20as%20to%20who%20owns%20the%20property%20at%20Ayodhya%2FBabri%20resulted%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20of%20November%209%2C%202019.%20While%20holding%20that%20pleas%20of%20title%20and%20adverse%20possession%20cannot%20be%20advanced%20simultaneously%20and%20from%20the%20same%20date%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20against%20the%20claim%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fplea-of-title-and-adverse-possession-cannot-be-advanced-simultaneously-162026%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emasjid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20directed%20that%20a%20suitable%20plot%20of%20land%20measuring%20five%20acres%20shall%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Sunni%20Central%20Waqf%20Board%20for%20construction%20of%20a%20mosque.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fayodhyatimeline%5C%22%3EAyodhya%3A%20Once%20There%20Was%20A%20Mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGhazala%20Wahab%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBorn%20a%20Muslim%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F997118%2Fby-accepting-land-in-lieu-of-babri-masjid-waqf-board-signals-that-muslims-dont-care-for-justice%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20articulated%20in%20an%20article%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi-Babri%20Masjid%20issue%20was%20never%20a%20land%20dispute%2C%20and%20if%20it%20was%20indeed%20a%20land%20dispute%2C%20then%20the%20litigating%20Muslims%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20have%20accepted%20alternative%20land%2Fmonetary%20compensation%20in%20lieu%20of%20the%20mosque%20before%20its%20mauling%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20accepting%20land%20in%20lieu%20of%20justice%2C%20Muslims%20have%20sanctified%20their%20secondary%20status%20as%20a%20community%20that%20does%20not%20need%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wahab%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Places%20of%20Worship%20(Special%20Provisions)%20Act%2C%201991%20preserves%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20every%20place%20of%20worship%20as%20it%20existed%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947%2C%20with%20an%20exception%20available%20only%20to%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2FRam%20Mandir.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20case%20held%20that%20the%20said%20law%20protects%20and%20secures%20the%20fundamental%20values%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eon-retrogression%20is%20a%20foundational%20feature%20of%20the%20fundamental%20constitutional%20principles%20of%20which%20secularism%20is%20a%20core%20component%E2%80%9D.%20Like%20many%20other%20legal%20scholars%2C%20former%20Union%20law%20minister%20Salman%20Khurshid%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fayodhya-verdict-ram-temple-salman-khurshid-6113623%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehailed%20this%20part%20of%20the%20judgment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20doctrine%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftranslaw.clpr.org.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FNavtej-Johar-v.-Union-of-India.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98non-retrogression%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20means%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20state%20should%20not%20take%20measures%20or%20steps%20that%20deliberately%20lead%20to%20retrogression%20on%20the%20enjoyment%20of%20rights%20either%20under%20the%20constitution%20or%20otherwise%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20quietus%20to%20all%20the%20ongoing%20or%20future%20litigations%20on%20account%20of%20the%20disputed%20nature%20of%20a%20place%20of%20worship%20would%20have%20been%20good%20for%20the%20fraternity%20of%20all%20Indians.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20when%20the%20Gyanvapi%20case%20was%20taken%20up%20for%20consideration%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20permitted%20the%20litigation%20to%20continue%20at%20the%20Varanasi%20district%20court.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fif-gyanvapi-suit-barred-under-1991-law-it-would-depend-on-its-character-as-on-aug-15-1947-says-sc-2726272%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20orally%20observed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20question%20as%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20%5Bthe%5D%20status%20of%20the%20place%20of%20worship%20%5Bwas%5D%20as%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947%E2%80%9D%20can%20be%20examined%20by%20the%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F23142008%2FGyan-vapi-mosque-min-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F23142008%2FGyan-vapi-mosque-min-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F23142008%2FGyan-vapi-mosque-min-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F23142008%2FGyan-vapi-mosque-min.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332680%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Kabir%20Agarwal%2F%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Krishna%20Janmabhoomi%20at%20Mat