0reigniting%20the%20ball-tampering%20controversy%2C%20claimed%20that%20Warner%20doesn't%20deserve%20a%20%26quot%3Bhero's%20sendoff%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20series%20being%20his%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2042-year-old%20had%20also%20taken%20shots%20at%20Australia%20chief%20selector%20Geroge%20Bailey%20for%20persisting%20with%20Warner%20despite%20his%20poor%20outings%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%20revealed%20that%20Warner%20texted%20him%20earlier%20this%20year%20after%20he%20wrote%20a%20column%20on%20the%20southpaw's%20wife%2C%20Candice%2C%20defending%20her%20husband's%20place%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20did%20not%20divulge%20much%20into%20the%20details%20of%20Warner's%20%26quot%3Bquite%20personal%26quot%3B%20text%20message%2C%20Johnson%20admitted%20that%20it%20was%20one%20of%20reasons%2C%20along%20with%20the%20ball-tampering%20scandal%2C%20behind%20his%20column%20of%20the%20West%20Australian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20a%20message%20from%20Dave%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20personal.%20I%20tried%20to%20ring%20to%20try%20and%20talk%20to%20him%20about%20it%2C%20which%20I've%20always%20been%20open%20to.%20I%20know%20I've%20been%20open%20to%20the%20guys%20when%20I%20finished%20playing.%20I%20said%20if%20I'm%20in%20the%20media%20and%20writing%20things%20or%20saying%20things%20that%20you%20don't%20like%2C%20just%20come%20and%20speak%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Australia%20pacer%20said%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fgb%2Fpodcast%2Fwhy-i-wrote-the-david-warner-article-and-my-reaction%2Fid1708567851%3Fi%3D1000637488804%5C%22%3EThe%20Mitchell%20Johnson%20Cricket%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20never%20a%20personal%20thing%20then%20until%20this%20point.%20This%20is%20probably%20what%20drove%20me%20to%20write%20the%20article%20as%20well%2C%20part%20of%20it.%20It%20was%20definitely%20a%20factor.%20Some%20of%20the%20stuff%20that%20was%20s