he%20principal%20deputy%20NSA%20raised%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiner%20also%20discussed%20with%20his%20Indian%20interlocutors%20the%20plans%20for%20a%20post-conflict%20Gaza%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bpathway%20toward%20a%20two-state%20solution%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20White%20House%20official%20met%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20NSA%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20and%20held%20extensive%20talks%20with%20Deputy%20NSA%20Vikram%20Misri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiner%20led%20a%20US%20delegation%20for%20an%20intersessional%20review%20of%20the%20US-India%20Initiative%20on%20Critical%20and%20Emerging%20Technology%20(iCET)%20with%20Misri.%20The%20two%20sides%20carried%20out%20the%20review%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20visit%20to%20New%20Delhi%20came%20days%20after%20American%20prosecutors%20linked%20an%20Indian%20official%20to%20a%20man%20charged%20with%20conspiring%20to%20assassinate%20Sikh%20separatist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20on%20Thursday%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmatter%20of%20concern%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20linking%20the%20Indian%20official%20to%20a%20man%20charged%20with%20conspiring%20to%20kill%20Pannun%2C%20and%20asserted%20that%20follow%20up%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20based%20on%20findings%20of%20an%20inquiry%20panel%20investigating%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20already%20constituted%20a%20probe%20team%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20charged%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%2052%2C%20of%20working%20with%20an%20Indian%20government%20employee%20in%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20kill%20Pannun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20readout%20said%20besides%20review%20of%20the%20iCET%2C%20Finer%20conducted%20bilateral%20and%20regional%20consultations%20with%20Misri%2C%20Minister%20Jaishankar%2C%20NSA%20Doval%2C%20and%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Kwatra%20for%20in-depth%20discussions%20aimed%20at%20strengthening%20%26quot%3Bcoordination%20and%20policy%20alignment%26quot%3B%20across%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20including%20the%20wider%20Indian%20Ocean%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20discussed%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20including%20the%20recent%20attacks%20on%20commercial%20vessels%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20safeguarding%20freedom%20of%20commercial%20navigation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20plans%20for%20a%20post-conflict%20Gaza%20and%20a%20pathway%20toward%20a%20two-state%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20been%20pushing%20for%20a%20'two-state'%20solution%20to%20the%20Palestine%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20address%20at%20a%20conclave%20last%20night%2C%20Finer%20said%20the%20US%20and%20India%20have%20established%20a%20mature%20relationship%20that%20enables%20both%20sides%20to%20identify%20opportunities%20and%20work%20through%20the%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20US%20and%20India%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplicated%20history%26quot%3B%20and%20they%20have%20not%20always%20been%20%26quot%3Bwholly%20aligned%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiner%20said%20there%20are%20many%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20issues%26quot%3B%20that%20remained%20in%20the%20relationship%20%26quot%3Bright%20up%20to%20the%20present%20day%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20said%20there%20is%20a%20bipartisan%20view%20in%20the%20US%20that%20both%20countries%20must%20seize%20some%20important%20opportunities%20that%20the%20world%20presents%20to%20the%20two%20sides%20both%20geopolitically%20and%20economically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20US%20and%20India%20have%20a%20complicated%20history.%20We%20have%20not%20always%20been%20wholly%20aligned.%20We%20have%20not%20always%20found%20it%20easy%20to%20work%20together%20as%20economic%20partners%3B%20we%20have%20not%20always%20found%20it%20easy%20to%20be%20on%20the%20sa