insider.com%2Fcheap-hotel-in-orlando-near-disney-universal-aventura-review-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehotel%20near%20Disney%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20then%20paid%20for%20parking%20and%20a%20rental%20car.%20Or%2C%20we%20could've%20tried%20squeezing%20into%20a%20double%20room%20at%20a%20Disney%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20we%20opted%20to%20pay%20a%20little%20more%20for%20a%20family%20suite%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Franking-popular-disney-world-resort-hotels-pros-cons-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney's%20All-Star%20Music%20Resort%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20two-bedroom%2C%20two-bathroom%20suite%20had%20everything%20we%20needed%3A%20beds%20that%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20wall%2C%20a%20kitchenette%2C%20and%20tons%20of%20cubby%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kitchenette%20wasn't%20really%20designed%20to%20fully%20cook%20meals%20in%2C%20but%20we%20made%20it%20work%20with%20our%20grocery%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20appreciated%20the%20Disney%20touches%20that%20came%20with%20our%20room%2C%20like%20the%20personalized%20welcome%20screen%20in%20our%20room%20and%20the%20s'mores%20and%20movie%20screenings%20each%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGenie%2B%20was%20worth%20the%20price%2C%20but%20we'd%20skip%20the%20Universal%20Express%20passes%20again%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20suggested%20we%20pay%20for%20Genie%2B%2C%20Disney's%20fast-pass%20system%20that%20lets%20you%20skip%20some%20lines%20in%20the%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrices%20vary%2C%20but%20Genie%2B%20can%20sometimes%20cost%20between%20%2415%20and%20%2435%20per%20person%20per%20day.%20It%20took%20us%20a%20bit%20of%20work%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20booking%20system%2C%20but%20avoiding%20long%2C%20hot%20lines%20with%20kids%20made%20it%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUniversal%20Studios'%20closest%20equivalent%20is%20Express%20Passes%2C%20which%20would've%20cost%20%24266%20per%20person.%20We%20chose%20not%20to%20buy%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20we%20had%20to%20wait%20longer%20for%20some%20Universal%20rides%2C%20we%20used%20single-rider%20lines%20for%20some%20to%20skip%20crowds.%20The%20only%20downside%20was%20we%20couldn't%20sit%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuilding%20a%20rest%20day%20into%20our%20itinerary%20was%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disney%20Parks%20Parade%20at%20the%20Magic%20Kingdom%20park%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20Resort.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e7751152bc2d00199139d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221997%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDisney%20World%20can%20be%20overwhelming%20for%20some%20families.%20%3Cp%3EHandout%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETheme%20parks%20make%20for%20some%20extra%20long%20days%20for%20little%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutting%20a%20rest%20day%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20our%20week%20gave%20all%20of%20us%20a%20chance%20to%20recharge%20by%20our%20resort's%20pool%20and%20spend%20time%20together.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20our%20money's%20worth%20out%20of%20our%20resort%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ffamily-money-saving-hacks-disney-world-which-work-fails-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaved%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20buy%20park%20passes%20on%20our%20rest%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20we'd%20visit%20during%20a%20different%20time%20of%20year%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Orlando%20is%20a%20hot%2C%20sticky%20mess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20drenched%20in%20sweat%20at%208%20a.m.%2C%20with%20heat%20indexes%20reaching%20100%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20by%20the%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I%20would%20go%20to%20Disney%20World%20in%20spring%2C%20fall%2C%20or%20winter.%20We%20might%20also%20be%20able%20to%20get%20lower%20prices%20that%20way%20since%20summer%20is%20one%20of%20Disney's%20most%20popular%20seasons.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe'd%20also%20change%20up%20our%20park%20itinerary%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225136%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20near%20Hogwarts%20Castle%20at%20The%20Wizarding%20World%20Of%20Harry%20Potter%20at%20Universal%20Studios%20Orlando.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e6623e4c17ff0019bb7047%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223444%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20family%20would%20like%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20at%20Universal%20Studios%20Orlando%20next%20time%20we%20visit%20Florida.%3Cp%3ESolarisys%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthings-i-never-do-at-disney-world-frequent-visitor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%20World%20newbies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20planned%20for%20two%20days%20at%20Magic%20Kindom%20to%20find%20our%20footing%20and%20take%20full%20advantage%20of%20the%20sprawling%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'd%20spend%20no%20more%20than%20a%20day%20there%2C%20return%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-during-full-day-at-animal-kingdom-travel-planner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnimal%20Kingdom%3C%2Fa%3E%20(my%20favorite!)%2C%20and%20then%20check%20out%20Epcot%20or%20Hollywood%20Studios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20also%20spend%20more%20days%20at%20Universal%20Studios%20on%20a%20return%20trip.%20The%20Wizarding%20World%20of%20Harry%20Potter%20is%20extraordinary%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20loved%20the%20Velociraptor%2C%20Incredible%20Hulk%20Coaster%2C%20and%20Bourne%20Stuntacular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20have%20time%20to%20do%20everything%20in%20Universal%20in%20just%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOverall%2C%20we%20enjoyed%20our%20trip%20but%20won't%20be%20Disney%20regulars%20anytime%20soon%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETheme%20parks%20are%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20experiences%20we%20want%20to%20expose%20our%20kids%20to.%20National%20parks%2C%20museums%2C%2