0I%20was%20surprised%20at%20how%20lightweight%20the%20formula%20felt%20despite%20being%20so%20nourishing.%20It%20left%20my%20parched%20hair%20feeling%20much%20softer%20%E2%80%94%20possibly%20due%20to%20the%20combination%20of%20safflower%20seed%20oil%20and%20lemon%20peel%20oil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20this%20product%20also%20offers%20heat%20protection%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20up%20to%20200%20degrees.%20It's%20also%20clear%20in%20color%2C%20meaning%20blondes%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20it%20affecting%20the%20tone%20of%20their%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20blondes%3A%20UNITE%20BLONDA%20Oil%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20purple%20bottle%20of%20UNITE%20Hair%20BLONDA%20Oil%20resting%20against%20a%20rock%20with%20a%20few%20drops%20of%20the%20oil%20around%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646542a1fb9a9d0018c8fe47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EUNITE%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20a%20natural%20blonde%2C%20have%20highlights%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdying-hair-platinum-blonde-tips-2018-3%5C%22%3Ebleach%20your%20whole%20head%20platinum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20paraben-%20and%20cruelty-free%20oil%20is%20specifically%20formulated%20for%20you.%20When%20I%20started%20noticing%20that%20certain%20hair%20oils%20seemed%20to%20make%20my%20hair%20look%20yellow%2C%20I%20switched%20to%20this%20product%20and%20very%20quickly%20saw%20an%20improvement.%20That's%20because%20it%20features%20a%20pale%20lavender%20color%20that%20helps%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fhow-to-fix-brassy-hair%5C%22%3Eneutralize%20brassy%20tones%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20boost%20the%20brightness%20of%20your%20tresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20this%20hair%20oil%20because%20it%20not%20only%20repairs%20and%20hydrates%20b