ould%20extend%20a%20soft%20loan%20of%20%24250%20million%20to%20Kenya%20for%20its%20agriculture%20sector%2C%20even%20as%20New%20Delhi%20also%20looks%20to%20procure%20Kenyan%20cheetahs%20and%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20two%20Indian%20nationals%20who%20went%20missing%20in%20the%20east%20African%20country%20in%20July%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20following%20discussions%20between%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Kenyan%20President%20William%20Samoei%20Ruto%2C%20who%20is%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit%20to%20India%2C%20the%20first%20after%20his%20election%20in%20September%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20confident%20that%20President%20Ruto%E2%80%99s%20visit%20will%20give%20new%20impetus%20to%20our%20bilateral%20relations%20as%20well%20as%20our%20engagement%20with%20the%20entire%20African%20continent%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases-hi.htm%3Fdtl%2F37336%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20Modi%20in%20his%20press%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20stated%20that%20India%20will%20provide%20%24250%20million%20as%20a%20line%20of%20credit%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmodernise%20Kenya%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20sector%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F37340%2FJoint%2BStatement%2Bduring%2Bthe%2BState%2BVisit%2Bof%2Bthe%2BPresident%2Bof%2BKenya%2Bto%2BIndia%2BDecember%2B0406%2B2023%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20a%20joint%20statement%20issued%20today%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Kenya%20has%20also%20offered%20%E2%80%9Cin%20line%20with%20Kenyan%20laws%2C%20to%20provide%20land%20to%20Indian%20companies%20and%20institutions%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20cultivation%20of%20crops%2C%20including%20millets%2C%20in%20Kenya%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20government%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20promised%20to%20urge%20Indian%20companies%20to%20invest%20in%20Kenya%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20sector%2C%20including%20in%20equipment%20and%20technology.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20total%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F37339%2FList%2Bof%2BOutcomes%2B%2BState%2Bvisit%2Bof%2BHE%2BDr%2BWilliam%2BSamoei%2BRuto%2B%2BPresident%2Bof%2Bthe%2BRepublic%2Bof%2B%2BKenya%2Bto%2BIndia%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efive%20agreements%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20signed%20today%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20standardisation%2C%20sports%2C%20culture%2C%20education%20and%20digital%20solutions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20the%20joint%20statement%2C%20a%20separate%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F37341%2FIndia%2BKenya%2BJoint%2BVision%2BStatement%2Bon%2BMaritime%2BCooperation%2Bin%2Bthe%2BIndian%2BOcean%2BRegion%2B%2BBAHARI%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ejoint%20vision%20statement%20on%20maritime%20cooperation%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20also%20released.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20India%20confirmed%20that%20New%20Delhi%20was%20hoping%20to%20get%20cheetahs%20from%20Kenya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20secretary%20Dammu%20Ravi%20said%20that%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20has%20expressed%20interest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20interest%20came%20only%20today.%20So%20we%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20take%20it%20up%20to%20them%20and%20pass%20on%20this%20request%20to%20them%20to%20see%20if%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20for%20cooperation%20in%20that%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%2C%20India%20had%20flown%20in%20eight%20cheetahs%20from%20Namibia%20and%20another%2012%20cheetahs%20from%20South%20Africa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20year%20later%2C%20six%20of%20them%20have%20died.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20three%20out%20of%20the%20four%20cubs%20born%20in%20the%20first%20litter%20to%20one%20of%20the%20cheetahs%20also%20did%20not%20survive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Findia-seeks-to-import-cheetahs-that-do-not-develop-thicker-winter-coats-to-prevent-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20been%20looking%20to%20get%20cheetahs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20do%20not%20develop%20%E2%80%98winter%20coats%E2%80%99%20during%20the%20summer%20and%20monsoon%20months.%20Apparently%2C%20the%20cheetahs%20imported%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%20exhibited%20this%20adaptation%2C%20developing%20%E2%80%98winter%20coats%E2%80%99%20during%20those%20months%20due%20to%20their%20natural%20habitat%20in%20the%20southern%20hemisphere.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKenya%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20around%20800%20to%201200%20cheetahs%2C%20is%20bisected%20almost%20equally%20by%20the%20equator.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20senior%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20official%20also%20stated%20that%20India%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20two%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20Zulfiqar%20Ahmad%20Khan%20and%20Zaid%20Sami%20Kidwai%2C%20who%20have%20been%20missing%20since%20July%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20issue%20about%20missing%20Indians%20did%20come%20up.%20As%20you%20know%20that%20this%20has%20been%20there%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%20The%20authorities%20on%20both%20sides%20have%20been%20in%20contact%20with%20each%20other%20and%20information%20was%20being%20shared%20between%20the%20two%20sides%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CBut%20at%20this%20point%20of%20time%2C%20we%20should%20not%20speculate%20because%20the%20investigation%20is%20ongoing.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20sub%20judice%20matter%20in%20the%20courts%20of%20Kenya.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20high%20commissioner%20to%20Kenya%20Namgya%20Khampa%20said%20the%20mission%20%E2%80%9Ccontinues%20to%20monitor%20these%20developments%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20engaged%20with%20the%20authorities%20in%20Kenya%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20two%20Indian%20nationals%20may%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20the%20disbanded%20Directorate%20of%20Criminal%20Investigations%20(DCI)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkenyan-presidents-aide-claims-missing-indian-killed-no-official-word-yet-from-govt-8227200%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20claimed%20by%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20the%20Kenyan%20president%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20as%20per%20official%20records%2C%20they%20continued%20to%20be%20missing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701800009000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05232723%2FModi-and-Ruto-II.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-250-million-soft-loan-kenya-cheetahs-missing-nationals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20loan%20is%20meant%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmodernise%20Kenya%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20sector%E2%80%9D.%20India%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20urge%20Indian%20companies%20to%20invest%20in%20Kenya%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-250-million-soft-loan-kenya-cheetahs-missing-nationals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Race%20row%20gets%20b