%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05142003%2Fimage-1576.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EDirectors%E2%80%99%20role%20on%20company%20boards%20has%20become%20more%20complex%20and%20demanding%2C%20especially%20for%20independent%20directors.%20Increasingly%2C%20they%20have%20to%20monitor%20and%20manage%20diverse%20stakeholders%E2%80%99%20interests%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20primarily%20focused%20on%20protecting%20shareholders%E2%80%98%20interests%20and%20expectations.%20In%20the%20context%20of%20banks%2C%20this%20was%20evident%20when%20an%20independent%20director%20of%20IndusInd%20Bank%20sought%20reappointment%20from%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reappointment%2C%20which%20had%20the%20support%20of%20the%20founders%2C%20promoters%20and%20the%20executive%20management%2C%20required%20the%20approval%20of%2075%25%20of%20voting%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%205%2C%202023%2C%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20shareholders%20rejected%20the%20reappointment%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketscreener.com%2Fquote%2Fstock%2FINDUSLND-BANK-LIMITED-9059225%2Fnews%2FIndusind-Bank-Limited-Announces-Cessation-of-Sanjay-Asher-as-Non-Executive-Independent-Director-45048079%2F%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Asher%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20senior%20partner%20of%20the%20prestigious%20law%20firm%20Crawford%20Bayley%20and%20Company%2C%20as%20independent%20director.%20This%20development%20should%20raise%20alarm%20bells%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20corporate%20world.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20shareholders%E2%80%99%20rejection%20was%20not%20based%20on%20any%20lack%20of%20competence%20on%20Asher%E2%80%99s%20part%2C%20but%20because%20the%20proxy%20advisory%20firms%20recommended%20his%20rejection.%20The%20proxy%20firms%20did%20so%20because%20Asher%20was%20a%20partner%20in%20a%20law%20firm%2C%20and%20he%20was%20equivalent%20to%20a%20whole-time%20(executive)%20director%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Securiti