0w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687763%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22369%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20IndusInd%20Bank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20name%20suggests%20that%20the%20committee%20is%20tasked%20with%20the%20concerns%20of%20stakeholders%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20to%20broaden%20its%20role%20to%20also%20include%20depositors%2C%20employees%2C%20regulators%2C%20proxy%20advisory%20firms%20and%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20banks%20play%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20SRC%20has%20to%20be%20strengthened%2C%20and%20members%20have%20to%20take%20a%20more%20active%20interest%20in%20its%20workings.%20Expanding%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20SRC%20will%20enhance%20its%20importance%20within%20the%20board%20and%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20private%20sector%20banks%2C%20the%20SRCs%20have%20failed%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20employees%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20high%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhemindrahazari.com%2F2023%2F09%2F05%2Findusind-bank-when-half-the-staff-left-why-didnt-independent-directors-think-it-worth-mentioning%2F%5C%22%3Eattrition%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2031%25%20to%2051%25%20in%20some%20of%20the%20banks%20in%20FY23.%20This%20concern%20has%20prompted%20the%20RBI%20to%20publicly%20express%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Frbi-closely-watching-high-attrition-at-some-private-banks-says-shaktikanta-das-18207931.htm%5C%22%3Eits%20apprehensions.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20SRCs%20need%20to%20be%20activated%2C%20and%20have%20to%20take%20cognizance%20of%20material%20information%20that%20is%20brought%20to%20their%20knowledge%2C%20including%20non-public%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20engaging%20and%20being%20receptive%20to%20stakeholders%2C%20the%20SRCs%20can%20adopt%20a%20forward-looking%20approach.%20To%20operate%20successfully%2C%20the%20SRCs%20would%20need%20to%20be%20more%20proactive%20and%20engage%20with%20employee%20representatives%2C%20which%20is%20difficult%20in%20many%20private%20sector%20banks%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20staff%20unions%20and%20officer%20associations.%20Seeking%20advice%20from%20proxy%20advisory%20firms%20and%20even%20analysts%20covering%20the%20concerned%20companies%20may%20be%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rejection%20of%20the%20renewal%20of%20the%20term%20of%20an%20independent%20director%20by%20IndusInd%20Bank%20shareholders%2C%20despite%20it%20being%20supported%20by%20the%20founder%20and%20the%20board%2C%20is%20a%20major%20embarrassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20renewal%20complied%20with%20regulatory%20norms%2C%20the%20rejection%20highlights%20the%20board%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20concern%20for%20current%20governance%20norms%2C%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20SRC%20in%20briefing%20the%20board%20regarding%20the%20concerns%20of%20proxy%20advisory%20firms.%20Company%20boards%20have%20an%20organisational%20structure%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20SRC%2C%20to%20address%20these%20issues%2C%20but%20this%20structure%20needs%20to%20be%20activated%20in%20order%20to%20improve%20governance%20in%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHemindra%20Hazari%20is%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20registered%20independent%20research%20analyst%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDISCLOSURE%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-attr%3D%5C%22not-done%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%2C%20Hemindra%20Hazari%2C%20am%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20registered%20independent%20research%20analyst%20(Regd.%20No.%20INH000000594).%20%3Cstrong%3EI%20own%20equity%20shares%20in%20all%20the%20companies%20mentioned%20in%20this%20report%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%3Cstrong%3EHDFC%20Bank%20subscribes%20to%20this%20analyst%E2%80%99s%20research%20and%20a%20member%20of%20this%20analyst%E2%80%99s%20family%20is%20employed%20with%20the%20bank%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Views%20expressed%20in%20this%20Insight%20accurately%20reflect%20my%20personal%20opinion%20about%20the%20referenced%20securities%20and%20issuers%20and%2For%20other%20subject%20matter%20as%20appropriate.%20This%20Insight%20does%20not%20contain%20and%20is%20not%20based%20on%20any%20non-public%2C%20material%20information.%20To%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%2C%20the%20views%20expressed%20in%20this%20Insight%20comply%20with%20Indian%20law%20as%20well%20as%20applicable%20law%20in%20the%20country%20from%20which%20it%20is%20posted.%20I%20have%20not%20been%20commissioned%20to%20write%20this%20Insight%20or%20hold%20any%20specific%20opinion%20on%20the%20securities%20referenced%20therein.%20This%20Insight%20is%20for%20informational%20purposes%20only%20and%20is%20not%20intended%20to%20provide%20financial%2C%20investment%20or%20other%20professional%20advice.%20It%20should%20not%20be%20construed%20as%20an%20offer%20to%20sell%2C%20a%20solicitation%20of%20an%20offer%20to%20buy%2C%20or%20a%20recommendation%20for%20any%20security.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20rights%20reserved.%20No%20portion%20of%20this%20article%20may%20be%20reproduced%20in%20any%20form%20without%20permission%20from%20the%20author.%20For%20permissions%20contact%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahkh%40hemindrahazari.com%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehkh%40hemindrahazari.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701770402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05142003%2Fimage-1576.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fwhy-indusind-banks-rejection-of-an-independent-directors-reappointment-raises-concerns%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20matter%20calls%20for%20reactivating%20the%20stakeholders%E2%80%99%20relationship%20committee%2C%20which%20has%20traditionally%20confined%20itself%20to%20shareholder%20grievances.%20As%20banks%20play%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20SRC%20needs%20to%20be%20strengthened.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fwhy-indusind-banks-rejection-of-an-independent-directors-reappointment-raises-concerns%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22German%20airport%20reopens%20-%20but%20flights%20'heavily%20restricted'%20after%20freezing%20rain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701770040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-flights-snowplough_6382753.jpg%3F20231205101306%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmunich-airport-reopens-but-flights-heavily-restricted-after-freezing-rain-13023284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Munich%20Airport%20has%20reopened%20with%20a%20severely%20reduced%20flight%20schedule%20after%20it%20was%20forced%20to%20close%20following%20a%20barrage%20of%20extreme%20wintry%20weather.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmunich-airport-reopens-but-flights-heavily-restricted-after-freezing-rain-13023284%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmunich-airport-reopens-but-flights-heavily-restricted-after-freezing-rain-13023284%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmunich-airport-reopens-but-flights-heavily-restricted-after-freezing-rain-13023284%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Flights%20impossible'%20as%20freezing%20rain%20and%20thick%20layer%20of%20ice%20forces%20German%20airport%20to%20close%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701770040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-flights-snowplough_6382753.jpg%3F20231205101306%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmunich-airport-forced-to-close-after-freezing-rain-and-wintry-weather-hits-germany-13023284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Munich%20Airport%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20close%20again%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20extreme%20wintry%20weather%2C%20making%20safe%20flights%20%26quot%3Bimpossible%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmunich-airport-forced-to-close-after-freezing-rain-and-wintry-weather-hits-germany-13023284%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmunich-airport-forced-to-close-after-freezing-rain-and-wintry-weather-hits-germany-13023284%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmunich-airport-forced-to-close-after-freezing-rain-and-wintry-weather-hits-germany-13023284%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Navigating%20Deception%3A%20Dissecting%20the%20Implications%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Guidelines%20on%20'Dark%20Patterns'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F05165453%2Fe-commerce-3576213_1280.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDark%20patterns%20refer%20to%20deceptive%20user%20interface%20designs%20employed%20by%20online%20services%20such%20as%20websites%20or%20apps%20to%20influence%20users%20to%20make%20decisions%20they%20otherwise%20might%20not.%20These%20misleading%20tactics%20are%20pervasive%2C%20extending%20from%20popular%20news%20websites%20to%20your%20favourite%20food%20delivery%20app.%20Virtually%20every%20online%20service%20incorporates%20some%20form%20of%20deception%20or%20user%20manipulation%20to%20enhance%20their%20profits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20this%20issue%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%20(DoCA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1955344%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520draft%2520guidelines%2520define%2520dark%2Cimpairing%2520the%2520consumer%2520autonomy%252C%2520decision%5C%22%3Eintroduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20Guidelines%20for%20Prevention%20and%20Regulation%20of%20Dark%20Patterns%20under%20Section%2018%20of%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%20of%202019.%20Their%20primary%20objective%20is%20to%20curb%20dishonest%20practices%20and%20promote%20transparency%20in%20the%20online%20marketplace.%20This%20marks%20a%20significant%20and%20commendable%20stride%2C%20considering%20that%20the%20Indian%20legal%20framework%20had%20been%20largely%20silent%20on%20the%20matter%20of%20dark%20patterns%20until%20now.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fconsumeraffairs.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Ffile-uploads%2Flatestnews%2FDraft%2520Guidelines%2520for%2520Prevention%2520and%2520Regulation%2520of%2520Dark%2520Patterns%25202023.pdf%5C%22%3Eguidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20define%20dark%20patterns%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cany%20practices%20or%20deceptive%20design%20patterns%20using%20UI%2FUX%20(user%20interface%2Fuser%20experience)%20interactions%20on%20any%20platform%3B%20designed%20to%20mislead%20or%20trick%20users%20to%20do%20something%20they%20originally%20did%20not%20intend%20or%20want%20to%20do%3B%20by%20subverting%20or%20impairing%20the%20consumer%20autonomy%2C%20decision%20making%20or%20choice%3B%20amounting%20to%20misleading%20advertisement%20or%20unfair%20trade%20practice%20or%20violation%20of%20consumer%20rights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposed%20guidelines%20are%20intended%20to%20apply%20to%20a%20broad%20spectrum%20of%20entities%2C%20encompassing%20sellers%2C%20advertisers%2C%20and%20platforms%20systematically%20providing%20goods%20and%20services%20in%20India.%20Notably%2C%20this%20extends%20beyond%20businesses%20physically%20located%20in%20India%2C%20as%20the%20guidelines%20also%20cover%20businesses%20operating%20outside%20India%20that%20target%20Indian%20citizens%20for%20the%20sale%20of%20goods%20or%20services.%20The%20discourse%20surrounding%20dark%20patterns%20is%20intricately%20connected%20to%20user%20autonomy%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20privacy%20framework.%20The%20use%20of%20dark%20patterns%2C%20leading%20to%20manipulation%20and%20diversion%20of%20attention%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20nullify%20user%20consent%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20unlawful%20collection%20and%20processing%20of%20personal%20data%20by%20platforms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20guidelines%20underscore%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20safeguarding%20consumer%20privacy%20and%20purchasing%20autonomy%20on%20the%20Internet%20by%20placing%20a%20significant%20focus%20on%20user%20interface%20design.%20This%20initiative%20is%20particularly%20pertinent%20in%20light%20of%20the%20relationship%20between%20dark%20patterns%20and%20user%20consent%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20privacy%20regime.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20guidelines%2C%20DoCA%20had%20already%20issued%20%E2%80%9CAdditional%20Influencer%20Guidelines%20for%20Health%20and%20Wellness%20Celebrities%2C%20Influencers%2C%20and%20Virtual%20Influencers.%E2%80%9D%20These%20guidelines%20outline%20specific%20responsibilities%20for%20influencers%2C%20emphasizing%20caution%20when%20making%20claims%20related%20to%20healthcare%20and%20medicine.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20guidelines%20state%20that%20the%20application%20is%20wide-ranging%20and%20thus%20for%20%E2%80%9Call%20platforms%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cadvertisers%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Csellers%E2%80%9D.%20It%20does%20not%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20define%20all%20the%20terms%20and%20makes%20vague%20references%20to%20the%20dark%20patterns%2C%20such%20that%20the%20applicability%20remains%20under%20question.%20However%2C%20the%20definition%20clause%20limits%20the%20meaning%20to%20as%20defined%20under%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20(E-Commerce)%20Rules%2C%202020.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20vague%20applicability%20and%20definitions%2C%20the%20penalty%20thresholds%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20clearly%20defined%20in%20the%20guidelines.%20There%20are%20no%20precise%20definitions%20of%20infractions%20or%20punishment%20criteria%20in%20the%20guidelines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20it%20stands%2C%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%20of%202019%20would%20impose%20severe%20fines%20on%20any%20of%20the%20dark%20patterns%20mentioned%20in%20Annexure%201.%20Non-compliance%20with%20the%20Act%E2%80%99s%20directions%20can%20lead%20to%20imprisonment%20for%20up%20to%20six%20months%2C%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20or%20both.%20Additionally%2C%20causing%20false%20or%20misleading%20advertisement%20which%20is%20prejudicial%20to%20the%20interest%20of%20consumers%2C%20is%20also%20a%20punishable%20offence%2C%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20up%20to%20two%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%20The%20imprisonment%20and%20fine%20increases%20for%20subsequent%20offences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELegislation%20such%20as%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(Reasonable%20Security%20Practices%20and%20Procedures%20and%20Sensitive%20Personal%20Data%20or%20Information)%20Rules%2C%202011%20(%E2%80%9CSPDI%20Rules%E2%80%9D)%20mandates%20the%20informed%20consent%20of%20users%20before%20collecting%20their%20sensitive%20personal%20data.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20newly%20enacted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwill-the-data-protection-law-empower-the-public%5C%22%3EDigital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202023%20places%20importance%20on%20obtaining%20explicit%20consent%20from%20the%20Data%20Principal%20before%20processing%20such%20data.%20Implicit%20or%20opt-out%20consent%2C%20lacking%20a%20clear%2C%20positive%2C%20and%20affirmative%20action%2C%20is%20not%20considered%20valid%20under%20these%20regulations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20global%20trend%20towards%20prioritising%20users%E2%80%99%20free%20and%20informed%20consent%20is%20evident%20in%20data%20protection%20laws%20worldwide.%20Various%20jurisdictions%2C%20including%20the%20US%20and%20the%20EU%2C%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20risks%20posed%20by%20dark%20patterns%20through%20legislation%20aimed%20at%20protecting%20both%20privacy%20and%20consumer%20rights.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20California%20Consumer%20Privacy%20Rights%20Act%2C%202020%2C%20and%20the%20California%20Consumer%20Privacy%20Act%2C%202018%2C%20recognise%20dark%20patterns%20and%20discourage%20their%20usage%20by%20rendering%20consent%20obtained%20through%20them%20invalid.%20In%20the%20EU%2C%20legislations%20such%20as%20the%20General%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%20the%20Digital%20Services%20Act%2C%20the%20Digital%20Markets%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20Unfair%20Commercial%20Practices%20Directive%20provide%20safeguards%20against%20manipulative%20tactics%20online.%20Notably%2C%20the%20French%20Data%20Protection%20Act%20resulted%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huntonprivacyblog.com%2F2023%2F01%2F06%2Fcnil-fines-apple-8-million-euros-over-personalized-ads%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%82%AC8%20million%20fine%20on%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20implementing%20the%20%E2%80%98personalised%20ads%E2%80%99%20setting%20as%20the%20default%20without%20prior%20consent%20and%20making%20it%20challenging%20to%20change%20the%20setting%20through%20multiple%20steps.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20guidelines%20must%20comprehensively%20address%20the%20myriad%20privacy%20risks%20associated%20with%20dark%20patterns%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20the%20unauthorised%20collection%20of%20excessive%20and%20unnecessary%20personal%20data%20without%20the%20informed%20consent%20of%20consumers.%20Even%20with%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202023%2C%20there%20remains%20a%20potential%20gap%20as%20it%20does%20not%20specifically%20govern%20the%20interfaces%20or%20designs%20responsible%20for%20collecting%20personal%20data.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnnexure%201%20of%20the%20guidelines%20serves%20as%20an%20indicative%2C%20though%20not%20exhaustive%2C%20list%20of%20dark%20patterns.%20However%2C%20recognising%20the%20evolving%20nature%20of%20deceptive%20practices%2C%20the%20guidelines%20should%20acknowledge%20the%20possibility%20of%20additional%20dark%20patterns.%20To%20facilitate%20this%2C%20consumers%2C%20civil%20society%2C%20or%20market%20players%20should%20be%20empowered%20to%20report%20new%20instances%20of%20dark%20patterns%20through%20an%20institutionalised%20feedback%20mechanism%20to%20the%20ministry.%20Once%20identified%2C%20the%20responsibility%20for%20limiting%20or%20discontinuing%20the%20deployment%20of%20dark%20patterns%20should%20squarely%20rest%20with%20market%20participants.%20This%20approach%20encourages%20industry%20self-regulation%2C%20with%20necessary%20oversight%20from%20the%20ministry%20and%20valuable%20consumer%20feedback.%20This%20collaborative%20effort%20ensures%20that%20the%20guidelines%20remain%20dynamic%20and%20responsive%20to%20emerging%20challenges%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20online%20consumer%20protection.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBhuvnesh%20Kumar%20and%20Sharad%20Panwar%20are%20fourth-year%20law%20students%20at%20National%20Law%20University%2C%20Jodhpur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701768637000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F05165453%2Fe-commerce-3576213_1280.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-guidelines-dark-patterns-implications%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20guidelines%20must%20comprehensively%20address%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20dark%20patterns%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20the%20collection%20of%20excessive%20and%20unnecessary%20personal%20data%20without%20informed%20consent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-guidelines-dark-patterns-implications%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Police%20'Harassed'%20Sikh%20Activist%20in%20UK%20Before%20His%20Sudden%20Death%3A%20The%20Guardian%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05140946%2Fkhanda.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Avtar%20Singh%20Khanda%2C%20a%20pro-Khalistan%20activist%20based%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20claimed%20just%20months%20before%20his%20sudden%20death%20in%20June%20this%20year%20that%20he%20was%20verbally%20harassed%20by%20Indian%20police%20who%20also%20threatened%20his%20family%20in%20Punjab%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fdec%2F04%2Findian-police-accused-of-harassing-sikh-activist-in-uk-before-his-sudden-death%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20agencies%20accused%20Khanda%20of%20radicalising%20Sikh%20youth%20in%20the%20UK%20with%20extremist%20and%20separatist%20ideology.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20the%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-security-barriers-uk-high-commission%5C%22%3Epulling%20down%20of%20the%20tricolour%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20in%20London%20during%20a%20protest%20by%20pro-Khalistan%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20investigation%20has%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20West%20Midlands%20police%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20claim%20that%20Khanda%E2%80%99s%20sudden%20death%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthorough%20review%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20there%20was%20no%20foul%20play%20suspected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhand%20died%20on%20June%2015%2C%20four%20days%20after%20he%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Birmingham%2C%20UK.%20He%20was%20recently%20diagnosed%20with%20acute%20myeloid%20leukaemia%2C%20an%20aggressive%20blood%20cancer.%20His%20associates%20suspected%20foul%20play%20%E2%80%93%20claiming%20he%20was%20poisoned%20%E2%80%93%20but%20British%20officials%20did%20not%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereports%20that%20the%20West%20Midlands%20force%20%E2%80%9Cappeared%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20its%20original%20statement%20to%20the%20press%2C%20when%20it%20said%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20%E2%80%98thoroughly%E2%80%99%20investigated%E2%80%9D.%20But%20the%20police%20say%20they%20are%20still%20%E2%80%9Csatisfied%20that%20there%20are%20no%20suspicious%20circumstances%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhanda%E2%80%99s%20friends%2C%20fellow%20Sikh%20activists%20and%20family%20members%20told%20the%20UK%20newspaper%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinsistence%20by%20British%20authorities%20that%20a%20deeper%20investigation%20is%20not%20warranted%20fails%20to%20take%20into%20account%20damning%20details%20that%20have%20emerged%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20global%20campaign%20of%20transnational%20repression%20aimed%20at%20Sikh%20separatists%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20is%20facing%20allegations%20that%20its%20agents%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-accuses-indian-government-of-assassinating-sikh-citizen-in-vancouver-expels-senior-diplomat%5C%22%3Einvolved%20in%20the%20killing%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20Canadian%20Sikh%20in%20Vancouver%20just%20days%20after%20Khanda%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20while%20a%20plot%20allegedly%20directed%20by%20an%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3Eidentified%20Indian%20government%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20to%20kill%20an%20American%20Sikh%20was%20thwarted%20by%20US%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20around%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3EFrom%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Khanda%E2%80%99s%20associates%20contradicted%20official%20statements%20that%20the%20death%20was%20investigated%20by%20West%20Midlands%20police.%20The%20police%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20take%20statements%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20after%20his%20death%2C%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20his%20employers%20or%20work%20colleagues%2C%20did%20not%20retrace%20his%20steps%20on%20the%20days%20before%20his%20sudden%20illness%2C%20did%20not%20visit%20his%20residence%20or%20study%20threats%20made%20against%20him%2C%20and%20did%20not%20issue%20a%20case%20number%2C%20which%20would%20indicate%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20investigated%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20report%20says.%20Khanda%20appeared%20%E2%80%9Chealthy%20and%20robust%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20weeks%20before%20his%20death%2C%20associates%20in%20Birmingham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%20and%20sister%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20they%20were%20the%20subject%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Caggressive%20intimidation%20campaign%20by%20Indian%20authorities%20in%20the%20months%20before%20%5BKhanda%E2%80%99s%5D%20death%E2%80%9D.%20While%20Indian%20agencies%20considered%20Khanda%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Amritpal%20Singh%2C%20the%20Sikh%20separatist%20and%20leader%20of%20Waris%20Punjab%20De%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famritpal-surrenders-himself-to-punjab-police-to-be-shifted-to-assam-soon%5C%22%3Ewas%20arrested%20in%20April%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20family%20%E2%80%9Cstaunchly%E2%80%9D%20denied%20any%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Amritpal%20Singh%20was%20on%20the%20run%2C%20Khanda%E2%80%99s%20mother%20and%20sister%20were%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fpunjab%2Fuk-based-activist-khandas-mother-among-3-detained-496763%5C%22%3Ep